19:10.236 --> 19:12.281
-Dr. Clark?
- Kurt!

19:12.325 --> 19:14.240
Did you see that?

19:14.283 --> 19:17.547
Dr. Clark, did you
see something down there?

19:17.591 --> 19:19.897
Based on its movements
and its speed,

19:19.941 --> 19:21.725
