impact study weeks ago.

19:30.778 --> 19:32.214
There should be
no large animals

19:32.258 --> 19:33.389
of that size down there.

19:33.433 --> 19:35.870
Riley, get back to CRATUS now.

19:40.048 --> 19:41.658
Kurt, what is this thing?!

19:46.446 --> 19:47.838
Kristy, what do you see?

19:47.882 --> 19:49.579
We see it on the scanner,

19:49.623 --> 19:51.320
