right behind you!

19:51.364 --> 19:53.235
You have to try and lose it!

19:55.585 --> 19:59.372
This thing is huge!
Much more than a hundred feet!

19:59.415 --> 20:01.417
Get back to CRATUS A.S.A.P.

20:01.461 --> 20:03.114
I can'’t shake it.

20:03.158 --> 20:06.030
All right,
give me a second to think!

20:06.074 --> 20:08.294
Whatever it is, do it fast!

20:08.337 --> 20:10.644
Um, try using
your drill'’s laser.

20:10.687 --> 20:12.298
Maybe you can
at least disorient it

20:12.341 --> 20:14.735
and get a chance to get away.

20:14.778 --> 20:17.433
Worth a shot.
Here goes nothing!

20:22.525 --> 20:23.700
Dr. Clark?

20:23.744 --> 20:25.180
Can you read me? Dr. Clark?

20:25.224 --> 20:26.747
I'’m here. I--

20:26.790 --> 20:29.010
I think I hit it
