22:48.105 --> 22:49.803
Dr. Clark...

22:49.846 --> 22:52.414
Kurt just told me
you saw a shark.

22:52.458 --> 22:53.415
Yeah.

22:53.459 --> 22:55.461
- At depth?
- Yeah.

22:55.504 --> 22:57.767
Well, I guess
that'’s not entirely uncommon

22:57.811 --> 22:59.421
