It did not show
a single animal

23:14.131 --> 23:16.090
in this zone of that size

23:16.133 --> 23:18.135
or any of the zones
that surround it.

23:19.354 --> 23:21.312
How big did you say
the shark was?

23:21.356 --> 23:24.054
It was approximately 187 feet.

23:24.098 --> 23:26.187
The blip was huge.
We both saw it.

23:26.230 --> 23:27.754
Wait.

23:27.797 --> 23:29.451
Earlier this morning,

23:29.495 --> 23:31.453
