24:18.718 --> 24:21.808
that that was extinct
3 1/2 million years ago.

24:21.851 --> 24:23.462
This thing came right at me

24:23.505 --> 24:25.855
and tried to take
a bite out of the sub.

24:25.899 --> 24:29.337
I nearly crashed the craft
trying to evade it.

24:31.557 --> 24:33.559
What about the CRATUS II?

24:33.602 --> 24:37.519
Well, we'’re recharging
the drill as we speak.

