25:28.265 --> 25:30.180
We'’ve got to protect this team.

25:31.312 --> 25:32.966
All right. I'’m on it.

25:33.009 --> 25:34.445
Follow me.

25:44.586 --> 25:45.979
Captain!

25:46.022 --> 25:49.330
I see a large object
heading on a westerly course,

25:49.373 --> 25:50.897
heading directly towards us.

25:50.940 --> 25:52.899
Fin in the water!

