26:16.444 --> 26:18.228
I don'’t want us wasting ammo.

26:18.272 --> 26:19.621
Copy that.

26:19.665 --> 26:20.883
- Oo-rah!
- Oo-rah!

26:20.927 --> 26:22.581
Eyes up, Marines!

26:22.624 --> 26:24.147
All hands!

