27:21.509 --> 27:23.946
Sure. No problem.

27:28.559 --> 27:31.040
Three-mile radius.

27:31.084 --> 27:32.433
Still nothing.

27:32.476 --> 27:34.391
Well, maybe it swam away.

27:34.435 --> 27:37.264
