31:31.846 --> 31:33.326
Copy that,Fragasso.

31:33.369 --> 31:35.589
We'’ll see you shortly. Over.

32:21.635 --> 32:22.984
Oh, God, shark!

32:23.028 --> 32:24.507
No, no!

